---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <h1>AI in Digital Humanities: Projects, Grants, Successes & Risks (2025–2026)</h1>

  <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 italic">
    Prepared for the Connecticut Digital Humanities Conference — March 2026
  </p>

  <h2>Executive Summary</h2>

  <p>
    Artificial intelligence has transitioned from an experimental auxiliary to a core methodological
    tool across the digital humanities landscape. The period from January 2025 through March 2026
    has been defined by major grant investments—most notably <strong>Schmidt Sciences' $11 million
    HAVI program</strong>—and landmark breakthroughs in manuscript recovery and archival access.
  </p>

  <h2>Report Sections</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose mt-8">
    <a href={`${base}funding/`} class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-stone-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-amber-300 transition-all">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">I. The Major Funding Landscape</h3>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Schmidt Sciences HAVI Program, NEH grants, and the current funding climate for DH projects.</p>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}transcription/`} class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-stone-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-amber-300 transition-all">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">II. Manuscript Transcription (HTR)</h3>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Handwritten Text Recognition advances including the CoMMA Project and Transkribus platform.</p>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}archaeology/`} class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-stone-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-amber-300 transition-all">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">III. Ancient Text Recovery & Archaeology</h3>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">DeepMind's Aeneas project, the Vesuvius Challenge, and AI-powered archaeological discoveries.</p>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}social-justice/`} class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-stone-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-amber-300 transition-all">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">IV. Social Justice & Underrepresented Communities</h3>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">AI tools for uncovering hidden histories and supporting indigenous language revitalization.</p>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}ethics/`} class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-stone-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-amber-300 transition-all md:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-2">V. Ethical Risks & Critical Perspectives</h3>
      <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Training data bias, cultural flattening, and the scraping crisis affecting GLAM institutions.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>
